title: Palces I want to go
name: Palces I want to go
description:
A Map by Hurricanes88

These are random places that I would like to visit in my lifetime.

properties.name: Australia
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88This would be an amazing place to visit. With the Outback, and the beautiful ocean.

properties.name: Brasil
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88I think that this would be an amazing place, because of the landscapes, people, and the women.

properties.name: Daytona
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88I have been here only once, and it was amazing!

properties.name: Fenway Park
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes881 fenway, boston, maI would love to see the Red-Sox play here. This is one of the most amazing places where i could think of going. All the history, the crowds, and the game of baseball would be amazing to experience here.

properties.name: Japan
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88I think that Japan would be a great place to visit because of their history and culture and would be an amazing place to eat new foods.I wouldnt enjoy the techno and anime though.

properties.name: Key West
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88It would be cool being the at the southern most point of the United States.

properties.name: London
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88I have never traveled outside the U.S. But London seems like it would be a very fun place to visit, with England being alot like the U.S.

properties.name: Manchester United
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88This would be an amazing place to watch soccer. Which to me is very underated in America and it deserves alot of respect.

properties.name: Miami Hurricanes
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88I would only go to Miami if i could see the Hurricanes play, they are my favorite team.

properties.name: Monterey, Ca
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88I have never been here, but i my girlfriend used to live here and tells me that I would really enjoy it.

properties.name: New Zealand
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88This would be an amazing place to go to. The Lord of the Rings was shot here, there was amazing landscapes in that movie.

properties.name: Ocean City Maryland
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88When i was younger, my family would vacation here. And i have not got to go here for about 4 years and I miss it alot.

properties.name: The Philipines
properties.description: Posted by Hurricanes88My dad went to the philipines when he was in the service and helped an orphanage there. I always have wanted to visit there since.
